22:36.939 --> 22:38.554
It affects everybody different.

22:38.732 --> 22:41.269
-How does it affect you?
-It depends.

22:41.569 --> 22:46.484
-Where I am, who I'm with.
-Well, you're safe with me.

22:47.324 --> 22:49.440
You gotta know that by now.

22:56.125 --> 23:02.212
Most folks use this for sex,
but it can take you much, much deeper.

23:02.798 --> 23:04.459
I get that.

23:05.634 --> 23:09.627
