magic you're already hooked up to.

23:09.805 --> 23:10.794
How do you know that?

23:10.973 --> 23:13.965
Because I care for people
who live in a different reality.

23:14.143 --> 23:16.054
That takes mad intuition.

23:17.813 --> 23:23.308
So you more like a shaman
in a Sunday hat.

23:23.986 --> 23:26.102
It's in you too.

23:26.822 --> 23:28.437
