to search for Edgington--

24:08.197 --> 24:10.688
Well, hey, Sam.
How are you this morning?

24:10.866 --> 24:15.030
-Reason the TV is so loud?
-Oh, fuck-a-doo.

24:15.204 --> 24:18.116
