but you did the right thing.

27:58.802 --> 28:00.417
No, I didn't.

28:00.596 --> 28:04.009
Look, I know how awful it is
to kill someone, but you have to remember--

28:04.183 --> 28:05.514
But I shot Eggs.

28:09.313 --> 28:11.395
He was coming after Andy with a knife.

28:13.275 --> 28:15.015
And I shot him.

28:15.611 --> 28:16.646
Dead.

28:17.696 --> 28:21.609
And I didn't tell you because
before I even had time to think...

28:21.783 --> 28:27.278
...Andy took over, and I ran, and I didn't
know which lies to tell you or Tara.

28:27.456 --> 28:29.447
SO I didn't tell you any.

28:29.958 --> 28:31.334
Tara's gotta know.

28:31.501 --> 28:34.789
People always find out,
and it hurts them ten times more.

28:35.631 --> 28:37.212
Like with Eggs, huh?

28:37.382 --> 28:39.498
You told him the truth,
and look what happened.

28:39.676 --> 28:42.053
-Jason.
-I'm good at protecting people.

28:42.679 --> 28:45.591
It's like the only thing I do right,
and that's what I'm doing.

28:45.766 --> 28:48.348
You're not protecting her.
You're lying to her.

28:48.810 --> 28:52.473
-And they ain't always so different.
-Yes, they are.

28:55.150 --> 28:57.015
How would you know, Sook?

28:57.194 --> 28:59.059
