30:35.250 --> 30:38.458
With those oils,
she saved many people from evil.

30:40.380 --> 30:42.245
[YELL]

30:48.930 --> 30:50.431
Whoa!

30:55.896 --> 30:59.184
[WOMAN SPEAKING IN SPANISH]

