Women from all over Mexico...

31:22.714 --> 31:25.956
...came to her for fertility problems.

31:27.969 --> 31:31.461
The egg will draw her essence up
and cleanse it.

31:31.640 --> 31:33.676
[BOTH LAUGH]

31:34.351 --> 31:39.015
-[IN NORMAL VOICE] How'd you do that?
-We're connected, bro.

31:41.108 --> 31:42.973
[VOICES SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

31:45.570 --> 31:47.071
[SPEAKS IN SPANISH]

31:48.407 --> 31:49.647
