32:34.202 --> 32:35.783
Damn.

33:10.614 --> 33:11.899
[IN JESUS' VOICE]

33:13.325 --> 33:15.441
[IN NORMAL VOICE]
Your grandfather?

33:20.332 --> 33:22.823
He practiced black arts.

33:23.376 --> 33:25.082
[IN JESUS' VOICE]
