33:33.887 --> 33:35.047
[YELLING]

33:35.222 --> 33:36.382
[BOTH GASP]

33:37.432 --> 33:38.547
[YELLS]

33:38.808 --> 33:42.346
It's Okay. It's Okay. It's Okay.

33:42.521 --> 33:44.682
What the fuck was that?

33:45.273 --> 33:46.774
That's my grandfather.

33:47.567 --> 33:50.104
A hechicero, a sorcerer.

33:51.363 --> 33:52.944
Shit!

33:55.408 --> 33:57.615
That was fucking awesome.

34:06.169 --> 34:09.878
-I know this is a dream.
-Well, you might as well enjoy it, then.

34:10.423 --> 34:12.880
Will your blood ever wear off?

34:13.218 --> 34:15.004
