35:32.756 --> 35:37.216
I'm sure it's gotta feel weird
having to do what you did.

35:38.595 --> 35:42.588
-Tara--
-You saved my life last night.

35:44.559 --> 35:47.175
You've been saving me
since I was a little girl.

35:47.354 --> 35:49.811
Yeah. That's what I wanna
talk to you about.

35:49.981 --> 35:54.850
See, sometimes when you try
and save people, you end up not.

35:55.862 --> 35:59.229
It's almost like your right hand,
it's not talking to your other hand.

35:59.407 --> 36:01.398
And you don't know
which one to listen to...

36:01.576 --> 36:03.783
...because they both
wanna do the right thing--

36:03.953 --> 36:05.238
Jason.

36:06.247 --> 36:08.738
I'm trying to say thank you.

36:10.627 --> 36:15.621
For last night, and letting me crash.

36:16.299 --> 36:20.383
You just get it.

36:22.597 --> 36:25.714
