36:25.892 --> 36:32.263
For some reason, you like pretending
you're too dumb to know better, do better.

36:32.440 --> 36:35.523
But you, you're good.

36:38.113 --> 36:40.195
I can count on you.

36:41.616 --> 36:44.107
And there ain't much of that
left anymore.

36:58.466 --> 37:00.252
[SOBBING]

37:00.510 --> 37:01.966
