that we restrain ourselves.

39:25.113 --> 39:27.024
-But--
-Even if it is against our nature.

39:49.012 --> 39:50.968
CHARLENE:
How many times you gonna count it?

39:54.225 --> 39:57.638
Until it stops being fun, sweetheart.

39:59.856 --> 40:01.938
CHARLENE:
It's all ours, babe.

40:03.651 --> 40:05.232
Come to bed.

40:15.872 --> 40:17.533
SAM:
Surprise, asshole.

40:19.542 --> 40:22.659
-What the fuck?
-Give me my money.

40:32.180 --> 40:33.420
Where's the rest?

40:38.853 --> 40:40.389
-It's in the truck.
-Get it!

40:44.734 --> 40:48.568
Give me your pants.
Give me your fucking pants!

41:00.541 --> 41:04.409
-What the fuck's taking so long?
-It spilled! Just give me a sec!

41:04.587 --> 41:07.203
You know, she told me all about you.

41:07.757 --> 41:11.170
After she'd fuck you, she'd come
crawling back into bed with me.

41:11.344 --> 41:13.710
She told me you like
to bark in your sleep.

41:13.888 --> 41:15.048
Freak.

41:15.390 --> 41:18.757
Yeah. Yeah, I am a freak.

41:18.935 --> 41:21.301
That makes it okay to fuck me over?

