No. NO!

41:43.084 --> 41:44.745
Hey, hey.

41:44.919 --> 41:49.083
Honey, stay with me.
Stay with-- Oh, God, no.

41:49.924 --> 41:52.040
No, don't you fucking die on me.

42:06.441 --> 42:09.399
[GROANING]

42:18.911 --> 42:20.651
Fucken

