42:58.242 --> 43:00.654
Deep down,
you know you shouldn't trust him.

43:00.828 --> 43:04.116
Okay. Tell me why.

43:07.710 --> 43:08.916
Well, here's the truth.

43:09.504 --> 43:12.371
There are forces beyond even my control.

43:12.548 --> 43:17.042
If I meet the true death without having
