43:20.306 --> 43:23.048
Why does it sound like
you're saying goodbye to me?

43:25.019 --> 43:26.099
Because I am.

43:45.957 --> 43:49.290
Okay, I get it.
I'm irresistible and intoxicating...

43:49.460 --> 43:53.499
