does not exactly help your cause.

43:54.048 --> 43:56.960
Tell me why I shouldn't trust Bill.

44:02.140 --> 44:05.257
-What?
-Blah, blah, vampire emergency, blah.

44:14.902 --> 44:16.403
This better be good.

44:16.571 --> 44:20.484
You're too busy signing wills and making out
