44:20.658 --> 44:23.024
There isn't any way to use her.

44:23.202 --> 44:24.703
It won't work.

44:24.871 --> 44:27.078
We know Russell wants her.

44:27.248 --> 44:30.490
-Give her to him to save your own skin.
-NO.

44:31.002 --> 44:35.041
He's gonna get her anyway,
sooner or later.

44:35.214 --> 44:36.294
No.

44:37.592 --> 44:39.173
I won't do that to her.

44:40.761 --> 44:45.801
You're choosing a human
over yourself, Eric?

44:45.975 --> 44:47.636
Over me?

44:47.810 --> 44:50.893
Your lack of sentiment has always
been your most admirable quality.

44:51.063 --> 44:52.348
