46:52.977 --> 46:54.433
Can we talk about that?

47:09.076 --> 47:11.237
You're a vampire
who chews on her fingernails?

47:12.913 --> 47:14.244
They grow back.

47:15.041 --> 47:16.531
I love you.

47:16.709 --> 47:19.451
I wanna be with you
for everything that you are.

47:19.920 --> 47:22.081
