47:22.256 --> 47:25.669
...because all you see now is the
quirky vampire girl who bites her nails.

47:25.843 --> 47:28.630
You're wrong. I broke up with Summer.

47:29.430 --> 47:32.513
I drove up to Caddo Lake,
and I spent all day asking God...

47:32.683 --> 47:36.346
...tO give me a reason
why we can't be together.

47:38.189 --> 47:42.933
And a hush came over the water,
and all the bugs stopped buzzing...

47:43.110 --> 47:45.101
...and it came to me.

47:46.655 --> 47:48.611
There is no reason.

47:50.326 --> 47:55.491
Hoyt, if you knew half the shit I'd done....
It's unimaginable.

47:57.958 --> 48:00.119
And I actually liked it.

48:01.796 --> 48:03.502
