48:08.969 --> 48:11.756
But don't tell me what I want
and what I don't want.

48:11.931 --> 48:14.673
That's my decision to make,
and I want you.

48:17.645 --> 48:19.226
Tell me you don't love me.

48:19.688 --> 48:24.648
Look me straight in the eye and say it,
and I'll leave you alone.

48:51.762 --> 48:52.968
Nice work in there, dude.

49:01.147 --> 49:03.012
