-She ain't with you?

49:58.162 --> 49:59.902
I've been looking everywhere, man.

50:00.080 --> 50:02.822
She's not answering her phone, nothing.
She left a note.

50:03.000 --> 50:06.367
-You promised me you'd look after her!
-Well, I did.

50:06.545 --> 50:09.753
You know better than anyone,
Sook's gonna do what Sook's gonna do.

50:09.924 --> 50:11.915
Ain't no man or brother's
gonna stop her.

50:12.468 --> 50:15.335
You gave me your word, Jason.
You have let me down.

50:15.513 --> 50:17.344
-And now--
-Jesus fuck!

50:17.515 --> 50:21.053
You think I don't know that?
Just shut your fucking mouth!

50:21.227 --> 50:22.433
And get out Of my house!

50:25.397 --> 50:28.889
Yeah. Sookie told me how that works.

50:29.068 --> 50:34.984
I take back whatever invitation you got
to come inside my fucking house!

50:36.492 --> 50:37.948
Motherfucker!

50:41.330 --> 50:43.070
[CLATTERING]

50:55.302 --> 50:58.009
[GROWLS]

51:08.023 --> 51:11.265
Oh, mama.

51:15.614 --> 51:18.071
I'm so sorry, Talbot.

51:18.617 --> 51:19.857
Tony.

51:20.953 --> 51:23.569
You're the strongest man
I've ever known.

51:23.747 --> 51:25.783
You made us a home.

51:25.958 --> 51:27.994
-You made us family.
-It was a nice house.

51:28.168 --> 51:29.669
-It was a home.
-Mm-hm.

51:29.837 --> 51:31.623
A haven.

51:31.797 --> 51:36.086
A refuge from all that madness.

51:36.260 --> 51:37.750
[RUSSELL SOBS]

51:42.641 --> 51:44.177
I told you, extra 500 to bite me.

51:52.109 --> 51:53.645
Oh, brother.

51:54.111 --> 51:56.067
It's all my fault.

51:56.947 --> 51:59.188
I will never forgive myself...

51:59.366 --> 52:05.077
...that in the end, you were so alone...

52:05.456 --> 52:09.916
...with no one holding your hand.

52:11.086 --> 52:13.202
Your beautiful...

52:14.214 --> 52:18.082
...beautiful hand.

52:23.557 --> 52:27.049
It is one thing
to face eternity without you...

52:27.561 --> 52:30.428
...but to have not been with you
at the true death....

52:32.149 --> 52:34.310
[SCREAMS]

52:39.573 --> 52:44.067
Talbot, you saved me from the world.

52:45.579 --> 52:46.910
From myself.

52:48.832 --> 52:51.118
I was a fool to trust him.

52:51.585 --> 52:56.625
And I am more sorry than I can ever say.

53:14.608 --> 53:19.477
I'm so glad we had a chance
to say our goodbye.

53:49.393 --> 53:51.634
-Where the hell have you been?
-I needed to think.

53:51.812 --> 53:55.304
I'm not some prisoner you can lock up
any time you feel like taking Off.

53:55.482 --> 53:57.393
Actually, you are.

53:58.026 --> 54:01.154
Ahh! Let me go!

54:04.658 --> 54:07.320
-I knew I shouldn't have trust you.
-You were right.

54:07.494 --> 54:09.655
Let me go!

54:09.830 --> 54:12.572
[GRUNTING]

54:20.632 --> 54:21.883
Eric!
